import { Card, CardContent, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Broucher = () => {
  return (
    <Grid container sx={{backgroundColor:'antiquewhite', padding:'30px 80px'}}>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={10}>
        <Card sx={{backgroundColor:'white'}}>
            <CardContent>
        <Typography>
            Download Broucher
        </Typography>
        </CardContent>
        </Card>
      </Grid>
      <Grid item xs={12} md={2}>
        <Typography>
            Download Broucher
        </Typography>
      </Grid>
    </Grid>
  )
}

export default Broucher
